Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:11.99,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro... Do you think the JASDF will win?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:13.49,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:20.49,Bullet_Main,tama,0000,0000,0000,,The fighting stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.12,Bullet_Main,tama,0000,0000,0000,,Did we win?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:44.29,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-That's... impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:19.10,Bullet_Ep_Title,ep 11,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(465,460)}#11 The Heart of Taurus, The Spear of Light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.67,Bullet_Main,hide,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}All hands prepare for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:24.13,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:25.72,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:31.75,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,A detachment...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:34.11,Bullet_Main,tama,0000,0000,0000,,No one else saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:36.63,Bullet_Main,tama,0000,0000,0000,,If they flank us, we're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.84,Bullet_Main,shou,0000,0000,0000,,However, leaving the camp would be a clear violation of our orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:42.88,Bullet_Main,shou,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do, Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:44.64,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:47.64,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll listen to our leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:55.40,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.65,Bullet_Main,hide,0000,0000,0000,,Leader Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.55,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going? \NReturn to your position!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:18.67,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:19.80,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:24.18,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tendo Martial Arts Sword Drawing \NFirst Style, Number 8:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:25.97,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Muei Muso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:34.31,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Kisara-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:42.07,Bullet_Main,fuse,0000,0000,0000,,Leader Satomi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:43.45,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,we've finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:47.01,Bullet_Italics,ren,0000,0000,0000,,We're strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.58,Bullet_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:56.38,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:09.60,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.50,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we're all done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.27,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:16.98,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, stay here and back me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.00,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.95,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and tell everyone to fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:25.97,Bullet_Main,hide,0000,0000,0000,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:29.28,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,if it isn't Leader Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:33.96,Bullet_Main,hide,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen the Spear of Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.38,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Spear of Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:39.46,Bullet_Main,hide,0000,0000,0000,,With that thing on their side,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:43.88,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,we never stood a chance from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:49.39,Bullet_Main,hide,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:51.24,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kokone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.75,Bullet_Main,hide,0000,0000,0000,,We were holding hands the whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:57.90,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,saying we'd be together until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:01.76,Bullet_Main,hide,0000,0000,0000,,And then the Spear of Light attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.64,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,The Spear of Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.57,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Alde... baran...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:47.91,Bullet_Main,civil,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.40,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gastrea are falling back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:01.67,Bullet_Main,tama,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:04.37,Bullet_Main,tama,0000,0000,0000,,Just how many people died?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.92,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Probably about half...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:09.41,Bullet_Main,tama,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy forces have \Nalso dwindled, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:12.72,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,But whatever they lost, they gained back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:13.39,Bullet_Main,tama,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:17.14,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Including both civil officers and JASDF,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:19.65,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,over a thousand have turned into Gastrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:24.59,Bullet_Main,tama,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning... there's only 500 \Nof us against 2,000 of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.20,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,It's a despairing number...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.13,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:44.71,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.84,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:49.86,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.59,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They gave it to me because I was helping!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.18,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.50,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you weren't in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.53,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.33,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,She holds the hands of the wounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:01.65,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,They all say she's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.39,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:05.57,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,I am being useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.90,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're amazing, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:11.63,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Rentaro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:12.95,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a beautiful night, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:16.43,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:19.54,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I was asked to supervise things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:23.12,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You won a spot in the shelter, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:25.78,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't win it; they gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:29.55,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,They said they couldn't allow the \Ngreatest brain in Japan to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:32.40,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I ripped it up on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:34.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You could've given it to someone if you \Nwere just going to throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:36.02,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,To who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:39.41,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If there were only a cup \Nof water in the desert,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:42.56,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,they'd just kill each other to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.00,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine we'd find
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:49.19,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,an oasis in the Tokyo Area that \Ncould quench everyone's thirst.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:51.32,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I'm here is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:54.91,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,because I wanted to cheer on \Nthe idiots who are trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:57.08,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,get out of the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:02.33,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were a much \Nmore logical person, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.03,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Humans tend to think logically,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:07.03,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but their actions are driven by emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:09.45,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Take action, Rentaro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:12.34,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stop, death will catch up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:14.74,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:16.79,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:20.85,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Also, about Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.33,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about her losing her \Nclassmates, I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.33,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite the tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:29.48,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, from a doctor's \Nperspective, how's Enju doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:35.26,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I think she's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:40.74,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Enju-chan's mental stability \Nis far stronger than we imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:42.18,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.56,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're a very skeptical man, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:49.49,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd avoid bringing up \Nanything that would remind her
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:51.28,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,of the incident, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:55.72,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,You two should go back and rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.51,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, this place is sort of creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:06.90,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the place, Rentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:10.77,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,According to what Shoma-nii \Nsaid, it should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:15.49,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome, Onii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:19.74,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,I've cleaned up this hotel, \Nso it'd be suitable for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:24.49,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Er, but we're only going to be \Nstaying here for a few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:28.63,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,Still, would it not make you \Nhappier if the place were clean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:31.50,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:34.72,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,we'd be lighting the fireplace \Nin the middle of summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:38.56,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the ashes from the Monolith \Nrising up and hiding the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.41,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,they say it'll be cold for the next three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:42.74,Bullet_Main,tama,0000,0000,0000,,Food's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:47.22,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.95,Bullet_Main,tama,0000,0000,0000,,See? Impressed, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.98,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Bro's the chef in our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:55.58,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,A pervert like you could never compare.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:59.24,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you really can't \Njudge a book by its cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:04.62,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.79,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Aldebaran run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:12.13,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of rumors going around, \Nbut nobody knows for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:15.28,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the Gastrea will attack again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.48,Bullet_Main,tama,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, there are \Nthree more days until the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:19.39,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,substitute Monolith is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:22.26,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun, do you have a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:24.90,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,I observed some patients
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:27.77,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,who had their arms or legs \Ncut off by the Spear of Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:31.98,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,All of them are experiencing \Ndeafness or loss of sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:35.11,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,which are symptoms of mercury poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:36.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Mercury?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:40.44,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-san, there's something I'd like to report
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.12,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,about that matter, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:46.09,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,During the battle, using Shenfield, \NI located a Gastrea,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:49.50,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,five kilometers away, that I \Nbelieve was shooting out mercury.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:50.87,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,What did it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.23,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:56.57,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shenfield doesn't have the \Nability to send images.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:59.76,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,However, it was rather large.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:03.26,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,I would say it was a Stage Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:04.76,Bullet_Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:07.66,Bullet_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Leader Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:09.85,Bullet_Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Gado sent out a summons for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:12.98,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please report to the temporary \Nheadquarters at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.29,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Gado?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.04,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.67,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:33.33,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:36.32,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it when I fought with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:39.09,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Aldebaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.57,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:44.26,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,However, it didn't take my leg;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.60,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I let 'im have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:53.10,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,How was my son, Hidehiko, \Nin his final moments?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:00.19,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,He fought very bravely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:04.19,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who had him \Nbecome a civil officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:09.45,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,If I had known this was going to happen, I'd have let him do what he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:14.52,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Gado, don't you think that the \Nenemy has too much of a lead on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:15.85,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:19.21,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,After the JASDF won the earlier battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:21.97,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,why did they lose so quickly this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:24.33,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,And when Aldebaran was hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:27.26,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,why did the surrounding Gastrea form a wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:30.27,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is... pheromones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:33.31,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying it's releasing pheromones?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:36.37,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that gathered the \NGastrea around Aldebaran was
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:37.75,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the aggregation pheromone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.89,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Aldebaran is using \Npheromones for various purposes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:43.03,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,to keep total control over the pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:45.26,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:47.87,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,if we defeat Aldebaran, \Nthe pack will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:49.33,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,We can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:54.33,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,That was a very helpful insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:59.34,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,But I will let you in on some information \Nthat you're not aware of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:03.29,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way to defeat Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:05.47,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,Aldebaran is immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:13.70,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,My Varanium blade split its head open
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.50,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,and pierced through upon reversal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:19.29,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure I dealt damage \Nto its brain and heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:22.07,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,However, it didn't fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:27.45,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,In the next instant, although slowly, \Nit began to regenerate itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:29.07,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:32.80,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not the only trump card they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:36.25,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,The Gastrea with the Spear of Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:40.80,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,It's been identified to be as \Ngreat a threat as Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:43.96,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,Codename: Pleiades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.46,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Pleiades...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:49.97,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot win simply by defeating Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:54.48,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we try to defeat the king, \Nthe queen will stand in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:59.73,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,In order to win this game, \Neliminating the queen is essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:05.99,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, we must make \Na very difficult decision today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:08.36,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,Leader Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:12.34,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,In the midst of maneuvers, \Nyou and your adjuvant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:14.18,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,strayed from Hidehiko's camp
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.91,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,and acted on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.33,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.20,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was to eliminate \Nthe enemy's detachment—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:21.54,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't change the fact \Nthat you disobeyed orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:25.83,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,Your actions were equal to fleeing \Nin the presence of the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:29.09,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,causing a potentially lethal \Ndisturbance in the civil officer ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:32.35,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,You must pay for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:36.11,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,Leader Satomi, I hereby disband your adjuvant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:37.85,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and sentence you to capital punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:39.60,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:52.20,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,Leader Satomi, are you \Nprepared to die once again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:55.96,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that if we can defeat Pleiades,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:59.85,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,we can find a hole in the wall \Nwe are currently up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:02.38,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:08.47,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to infiltrate enemy \Nterritory and destroy Pleiades.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:11.11,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You've shown your true colors...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:13.38,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:19.23,Bullet_Main,gado,0000,0000,0000,,In return, I promise your \Nadjuvant will not be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.60,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You conniving old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:33.63,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Enju.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.61,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Satomi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.21,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,To the bathroom. \NAre you going to follow me there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.32,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,With all that luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.97,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I can bring whatever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:55.53,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,So the punishment wasn't just the \Ndisbanding of the adjuvant, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.78,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,But by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.54,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same as going off to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:03.48,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Someone has to take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:08.98,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:12.74,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.74,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:18.23,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere left to run in the Tokyo Area.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:22.19,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't stop it here, we'll die, \Nno matter where we run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:24.25,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one thing we have to avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.49,0:16:27.35,Bullet_Main,reen,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kisara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:33.37,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,You really are
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.60,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.90,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:16.21,Bullet_Main,hiru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fancy meeting you here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:17.40,Bullet_Main,hiru,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:19.39,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,So you were alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:22.30,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Hiruko Kagetane!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.92,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Would you kindly put your gun down already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:31.92,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:38.80,Bullet_Main,hiru,0000,0000,0000,,Have you already forgotten who it was \Nthat gave you bandages and antibiotics?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:42.93,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,And you guys haven't forgotten \Nwhat you've done, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.14,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:48.06,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Are you involved in that \Ngeezer's schemes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:50.95,Bullet_Main,hiru,0000,0000,0000,,I have no comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.56,Bullet_Main,kohi,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Enju?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.93,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.82,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,She's alive. We're moving separately for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:19:00.05,Bullet_Main,kohi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good! Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:01.46,Bullet_Main,kohi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:02.90,Bullet_Main,kohi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cut her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:05.33,Bullet_Main,kohi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see her... I want to cut her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.74,Bullet_Main,kohi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I want to see her... I want to cut her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:09.40,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun, one could ask \Nwhat it is you're doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.58,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to defeat Pleiades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.07,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Pleiades?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:15.25,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Gastrea that shoots out mercury.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:18.51,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I did see something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:21.76,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching the battle yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:23.57,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:25.58,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:28.47,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,What, exactly, waits \Nfor me after this battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:29.98,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.48,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,I've never wished for such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.48,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You truly are broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:41.24,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever even considered me normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:47.41,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you wear a mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:52.67,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to see my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:54.79,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:56.27,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,That is the correct answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:59.30,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,You would assuredly regret seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.43,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scarred or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.35,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,The thing under this mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:08.14,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,is your own face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.77,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:13.67,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,We possess powers that are beyond humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:18.73,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,When faced with senseless violence, \Nyou must have thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:25.31,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,"I have enough power inside me \Nto turn you all into ground meat!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:28.80,Bullet_Main,kagee,0000,0000,0000,,I've been carrying that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:31.92,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:34.76,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,You envy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:35.79,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:37.74,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,However, Satomi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:42.31,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you feel about me, I, too, envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.80,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Living so comfortably in \Nyour world of light...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:48.16,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but despise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:52.08,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:55.06,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,I shall teach you pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:21:00.57,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I will never mistake how I use my powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.76,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,I shall make a prediction, Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:10.20,Bullet_Main,kagee,0000,0000,0000,,You will definitely come to this side...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:12.96,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:27.04,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Did they already leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:33.99,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,A river...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:36.60,Bullet_Main,kagee,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:39.61,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:44.86,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,We happened to bump into this \NGastrea named Pleiades yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:45.86,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:49.37,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Follow the river upstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.32,0:21:52.62,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:21:56.15,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I must give a reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:58.53,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,it might be because I happen to like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:04.88,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.06,0:22:09.01,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,You just happen to be \Ngoing the same way we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.63,0:22:12.10,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.89,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,And that's precisely what we shall do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:39.69,Bullet_Next_Ep_Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,#12 Crisis Point
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:32.59,Bullet_Main,hiruko,0000,0000,0000,,This is the world that you wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:34.56,Bullet_Main,hiruko,0000,0000,0000,,You must make amends with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:36.68,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Please, Satomi-kun. Lead us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:39.25,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,The final battle will be at \Nthe Flames of Revolution.
